Serializable, Cloneable, Observer, IDecisionInteractive, IDecisionMethod, IDecisionMethodPrority, XMLSerializable
public class CramerRules
extends UserDefinedTree

An UserDefinedTree descendant, implementing the decision tree described in "Cramer G. M., R. A. Ford, R. L. Hall, Estimation of Toxic Hazard - A Decision Tree Approach, J. Cosmet. Toxicol., Vol.16, pp. 255-276, Pergamon Press, 1978".
Uses all IDecisionRule rules in toxTree.tree.cramer package Assigns categories:

  • CramerClass1
  • CramerClass2
  • CramerClass2
